media:group.media:title: Vikings - Through the Ages (1999 vs 2022)
media:group.media:description:
Part six of a mini-series looking back at the changes made to the original civilizations in Age of Kings. The focus this time is on Vikings.

0:15 Vikings in 1998
1:25 Vikings in Age of Kings
3:32 Conquerors Expansion (2000)
5:44 The Forgotten (2013)
6:40 African Kingdoms (2015)
7:50 Rise of the Rajas (2016)
8:20 Definitive Edition (2019)
8:52 Dawn of the Dukes (2021)
10:18 Current statistics (2022)
